qas.question: What does every cardinal priest not have?

plausible_answers.text: all administrative rights cardinals had with regard to their titular churches

qas.question: What did Pope Paul V abolish?

plausible_answers.text: the cardinal's name and coat of arms

qas.question: What is not still posted in the church after Pope Paul VI abolished all administrative rights?

plausible_answers.text: celebrate mass and preach there if convenient when they are in Rome.
